  "title": "HR Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Recruitment</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Coordinate job postings and manage applicant submissions</li>\n  <li>Prepare pre-employment documents &amp; ensure completeness of application submissions</li>\n  <li>Liaise with clients for candidate approvals including submission and follow-ups</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Onboarding</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Handle work pass process</li>\n  <li>Prepare and explain employment contracts and follow up on signed LOAs &amp; Addendums</li>\n  <li>Create and maintain employee P-files</li>\n  <li>Arrange agreements for onboarding ( PPE &amp; Company assets )</li>\n  <li>Set up new joiner accounts under HRIS and conduct pre-commencement briefings</li>\n  <li>Notification to site admin/client on commencement dates</li>\n  <li>Conduct orientation &amp; track/ follow up on signed onboarding documents and orientation forms</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Operations</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Manage staff movement ( New join/resigned staff/transfer staff etc) &amp; update monthly manpower report</li>\n  <li>Support in payroll process ( i.e HR/finance report, masterlist, payslip etc) </li>\n  <li>Manage leave records, approvals, notifications and acknowledgements</li>\n  <li>Source &amp; arrange stand-in, inform client/site/finance department </li>\n  <li>Dissemination, aknowledgement and keeping record of signed policies </li>\n  <li>Handle staff enquiries/grievances/ disciplinary cases </li>\n  <li>Managing appraisal (if required) </li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Training</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Verify that employees possess required certifications and coordinate relevant training courses to ensure compliance with requirements</li>\n  <li>seek management approval for training arrangement and handle course registration to ensure compliance and workforce readiness.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Offboarding </strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Collect resignation reason and formal acknowledgement </li>\n  <li>Notify internal and client/site teams of departure </li>\n  <li>Check through final timesheet submission </li>\n  <li>Manage offboarding checklist and handover process</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements: </strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma or Degree in HRM, Business Administration or related field </li>\n  <li>Minimum 2 years of relevant HR Experience, preferably in a generalist or operations role </li>\n  <li>Experience handling multi-site or client- facing HR coordination</li>\n  <li>Familiarity with Singapore employment laws and statutory requirements </li>\n  <li>Proactive and able to work in a fast paced environment </li>\n  <li>High Attention to detail and accuracy</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>",
